@node About
================================
 About PalmDoc
================================

This project is my second attempt at writing something in Gui4Cli,
the first was PalmSyncGC, a simple but very useful GUI interface to
Richard Koerber's shell-based Palm hotsync tool. You may note a Palm
theme creeping in ;-)

I own a Palm Pilot Pro and use the PalmLink and PalmTransfer software
(with my own PalmSync GUI) to sync data between Amiga and Palm. Some
of that data consists of DOC files, usually text files converted to
the format via Bill Chin's Amiga port of Kadar Tanuwidjaja's Makedoc.

Converting to/from DOCs using the shell can be laborious at times, so
I had a quick go at writing a Gui4Cli front-end, and this is the
result. It only converts to DOC format at present, and doesn't support
changing the category or modification of existing DOC .pdb files. I've
never used the last two features anyway, so they weren't a priority.
It's a start anyway.

Hope you find it as useful as I do...

@endnode
