===============================
 Requirements
===============================

MakeDoc by Bill Chin / Kadar Tnuwidjaja
Gui4Cli by Dimitris Keletsekis


Gui4Cli is available from The Gui4Cli WWW Page:
 http://users.hol.gr/~dck/gcmain.htm

Makedoc is available from Aminet:
 /util/conv/makedoc-palm.lha


@endnode
@node Installation
===============================
 Installation
===============================

Copy PalmDoc.gc and its icon to a location of your choice.

It's as simple as that, assuming you have Gui4Cli and Makedoc
already installed. Ensure Makedoc is in your path (I keep mine in
C:)

@endnode
